article.description: — Parker Braun had 19 points as Santa Clara easily defeated Nevada 96-74 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Braun carries Santa Clara over Nevada 96-74
article.linkText: Braun carries Santa Clara over Nevada 96-74
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- — Parker Braun had 19 points as Santa Clara easily defeated Nevada 96-74 on Tuesday night. Keshawn Justice and Jalen Williams added 18 points each for the Broncos. Braun hit 9 of 10 shots. He added three blocks. Justice also had eight rebounds. PJ Pipes had 12 points for Santa Clara (3-0). Grant Sherfield had 23 points and six assists for the Wolf Pack (1-2). Desmond Cambridge Jr. added 18 points.
